    <abstract>
      <t>   This document defines YANG data modules augmenting the IETF IS-IS
   YANG model to provide support for IS-IS Minimum Remaining Lifetime as
   defined in RFC 7987, and IS-IS Application-Specific Link Attributes
   as defined in RFC 8919.

	 </t>
